<DialogueTree xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xen-42/outer-wilds-new-horizons/main/NewHorizons/Schemas/dialogue_schema.xsd">
  <NameField>Slate</NameField>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>Start</Name>
    <EntryCondition>DEFAULT</EntryCondition>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>Oh, why are you still here? Did you get the <![CDATA[<color=orange>new launch codes</color>]]> yet?</Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>Is that the anglerfish from the museum?</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>3</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text><![CDATA[<color=orange>Ernesto</color>]]>?! NO!</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>2</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>2</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>Who is <![CDATA[<color=orange>Ernesto</color>]]>?</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>The anglerfish from the museum exhibition. Hornfels named it that.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>3</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>


  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>3</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>Okay, you know what? Yes, it is the anglerfish from the museum. I'm fed up with marshmallow. I can't take it anymore.</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>So you decided to eat <![CDATA[<color=orange>Ernesto</color>]]>?! Hornfels said <![CDATA[<color=orange>Ernesto</color>]]> is a friend!</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>4</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>4</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>Anglerfish is still a fish. Whatever he calls it, is almost done cooking.<![CDATA[<Pause=1>]]>.<![CDATA[<Pause=1>]]>.<![CDATA[<Pause=1>]]> or not. I think it will be prepared in like <![CDATA[<i>30 minutes</i>]]>. Why don't you fly near <![CDATA[<color=orange>Dark Bramble</color>]]> and just get a new one for Hornfels?</Page>
    </Dialogue>
    <DialogueOptionsList>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>I'll do that! <![CDATA[<i>(actually not)</i>]]></Text>
        <DialogueTarget>END</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>That's disgusting.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>END2</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
      <DialogueOption>
        <Text>Nah, enjoy your meal then.</Text>
        <DialogueTarget>END3</DialogueTarget>
      </DialogueOption>
    </DialogueOptionsList>
  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>END</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>You'll do that for me? Thanks! Just don't tell anyone about <![CDATA[<color=orange>Ernesto</color>]]> alright?</Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <RevealFacts>
      <FactID>ERNESTO_POOR_ERNESTO</FactID>
      <FactID>ERNESTO_FOUND_RUMOR</FactID>
    </RevealFacts>

  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>END2</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>There is no accounting for tastes.</Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <RevealFacts>
      <FactID>ERNESTO_POOR_ERNESTO</FactID>
      <FactID>ERNESTO_FOUND_RUMOR</FactID>
    </RevealFacts>

  </DialogueNode>

  <DialogueNode>
    <Name>END3</Name>
    <Dialogue>
      <Page>Thank you! Get back within <![CDATA[<i>30 minutes</i>]]> and I'll give you a bite.</Page>
    </Dialogue>

    <RevealFacts>
      <FactID>ERNESTO_POOR_ERNESTO</FactID>
      <FactID>ERNESTO_FOUND_RUMOR</FactID>
    </RevealFacts>

  </DialogueNode>
</DialogueTree>